Steps for Kali Linux

Install UFW (for installation):
We have to enter into root user for installation purposes
(use sudo root)

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ufw -y


Enable UFW:
(use this command)
sudo ufw enable


Allow SSH :
(use this command)
sudo ufw allow ssh


Add example rules:

Allow HTTP (80):

sudo ufw allow 80/tcp


Block FTP (21):

sudo ufw deny 21/tcp


Check rules:

sudo ufw status numbered
